      "text": [
        " رِوَايَةِ حَرِيزٍ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : فِي رَجُلٍ قَدِمَ مَكَّةَ فِي وَقْتِ اَلْعَصْرِ فَقَالَ «يَبْدَأُ بِالْعَصْرِ ثُمَّ يَطُوفُ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3119 - In a narration from Hariz, from Abu Abdullah (as), regarding a man who arrives in Mecca at the time of Asr prayer,\nImam (as) said: \"He should begin with the Asr prayer and then perform Tawaf.\""
        ]
      }
    },
